Howdy from Harrisburg!  I would like to apologize for shirking my blogging responsibilities regarding the <i>Kitzmiller</i> case -- NCSE is consulting for the plaintiffs, talking to the media, and hopefully blogging, but doing the first two has excluded the latter until now.  We did get a chance to do some podcasting, which I believe Wes has put up.

