For more excellent coverage, see <a href="http://ydr.com/news/doverbiology/">Dover Biology</a> at the always-on-top of things <i>York Daily Record</i>, particularly Lauri Lebo's story "<a href="http://ydr.com/news/doverbiology/">Witness bashes intelligent design</a>."  See also Mike Argento's blog commentary at http://www.yorkblog.com/.
